《'''年轻气盛'''》（{{lang-it|La giovinezza}}）是意大利导演[[保罗·索伦蒂诺|保罗·索伦蒂诺]]编剧并执导的一部英语电影。[[米高·肯恩|米高·肯恩]]、[[麗素·慧絲|麗素·慧絲]]、[[保羅·達諾|保羅·達諾]]、[[珍·芳達|珍·芳達]]和[[哈维·凯特尔|哈维·凯特尔]]主演。<ref name=guardian>{{cite news|last1=Child|first1=Ben|title=Sorrentino's The Early Years stars Michael Caine as conductor compelled to perform for the Queen|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/may/13/paolo-sorrentino-the-early-years-michael-caine-queen-rachel-weisz|accessdate=20 December 2014|work=The Guardian|date=13 May 2014|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220124130/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/may/13/paolo-sorrentino-the-early-years-michael-caine-queen-rachel-weisz|dead-url=no}}</ref>入选[[第68届坎城影展|第68届坎城影展]]主竞赛片。<ref name="Cannes">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/article/61306.html |title=2015 Official Selection |accessdate=16 April 2015 |work=Cannes |archive-date=2015-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418084150/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/article/61306.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/61347.html|title=Screenings Guide|work=Festival de Cannes|date=6 May 2015|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518080922/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/61347.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>赢得[[第28届欧洲电影奖|第28届欧洲电影奖]]最佳影片、最佳导演和最佳男主角三个奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1905.com/news/20151213/958127.shtml |language= |title=欧洲电影奖揭晓 《年轻气盛》夺得三奖成大赢家 |publisher=1905电影网 |date=2015-12-13 |accessdate= |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222122958/http://www.1905.com/news/20151213/958127.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==剧情==
一位退休的[[指挥家|指挥家]]弗雷德与朋友米克和女儿莉娜在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[阿尔卑斯山|阿尔卑斯山]][[度假|度假]]，此时他收到了来自于英女王[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]的邀请，请他为[[爱丁堡公爵菲利普亲王|菲利普亲王]]的生日指挥一场音乐演出。女儿莉娜的婚姻触礁，导演米克则与编剧团队正构思拍摄一部新片《生命的最后一日》，计划邀请老搭档布兰达主演。

