==制作==
2014年5月在[[瑞士|瑞士]]开拍。<ref name="guardian"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lyman|first1=Eric|title=Paulo Sorrentino's 'The Early Years' Begins Shooting, Storyline Revealed|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/paulo-sorrentinos-early-years-begins-703233|website=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=20 December 2014|date=5 May 2014|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613030918/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/paulo-sorrentinos-early-years-begins-703233|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些片段在[[罗马|罗马]]拍摄<ref>{{cite web|title=Paolo Sorrentino and Rome|url=http://www.janefonda.com/paolo-sorrentino-rome/|publisher=JaneFonda.com|accessdate=20 December 2014|date=11 July 2014|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618153146/http://www.janefonda.com/paolo-sorrentino-rome/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是保罗·索伦迪诺执导的第二部英语电影。

== 评价 ==
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]新鲜度72%，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到63分，获得大多好评。

[[网易|网易]]影评：“华美的视听，精致、情绪饱满并不空洞的形式符号，智慧的台词文本，有力支撑着导演要传达的思考。如何在时间的流逝中，看待过去与未来之间的远近虚实，找回生活最本真简单的美，并摒弃繁杂找到最深层真切的觉知，是《年轻气盛》带个人们的一番感受与思考。”<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0521/08/AQ4IV4RN00034VAQ.html |language= |title=《年轻气盛》：用绝美唱出极简的人生之歌 |publisher=网易娱乐 |date=2015-05-21 |accessdate= |archive-date=2015-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524061726/http://ent.163.com/15/0521/08/AQ4IV4RN00034VAQ.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

